nd-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">18000</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">40</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">3</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">2</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">2</td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30"><br/></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30"><br/></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">合计</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">538</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">54</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">27</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">27</td></tr></tbody></table><p>四、招生专业、专业招生计划及学费标准</p><p>五、 志愿填报</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px;">通过资格审核的考生于 2021 年 4 月 25 日 9：00-2021 年 4 月 28 日 17：00 登录江西省教育考试院网（网址：www.jxeea.cn）“专升本报考系统”，根据我校招生章程中明确的招生计划、专业及有关要求，对照《江西省 2021 年普通高校专升本对应专业指导目录》选择报考志愿。每个考生选报 1 所高校和 1 个专业类的招生专业。本次网报期间，考生所报志愿允许修改一次，逾期不予以办理。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px;">考生网上志愿填报成功后，须网上自行打印报名表，并于 6 月2-4 日领取准考证时上交报考高校，同时向我校财务处缴纳专升本报名考试费 130 元/人（收费标准依据省发改委《关于核定我省普通高校专升本报名考试费收费标准的复函》）。</p><p>六、考试时间、科目</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px;">（一）考试时间：2021 年 6 月 5 日</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px;">公共基础科目考试时间为上午 9:00-11:30</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px;">专业基础科目考试时间为下午 13:00-15:00</p><p>（二）考试科目：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px;">公共基础科目（政治+英语+信息技术三门综合卷）由省教育考试院统一组织命题、制卷，卷面满分值 300 分；专业基础科目由我校自行命题、制卷，卷面满分值 150 分。各专业考试科目如下表，考试大纲可下载网址（www.jxuspt.com）。</p><p>各专业考试科目一览表</p><table width="1160"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;" class="firstRow"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">序号</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">专业</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">专业科目</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30">公共基础科目</td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: top; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(